items.title: Maddon honored by Rays in return to St. Pete
items.summary: Joe Maddon returned to Tropicana Field on Tuesday night. The Rays' icon fashioned a Cubs uniform, bringing along his customary smile and ingratiating manner to the place where he helped produce magic as Tampa Bay's manager.
items.content: Joe Maddon returned to Tropicana Field on Tuesday night. The Rays' icon fashioned a Cubs uniform, bringing along his customary smile and ingratiating manner to the place where he helped produce magic as Tampa Bay's manager.
